{"tid":1845304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本最快明天派包機到武漢接走國民","createTime":"2020-01-27T05:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T06:55:55.000Z","uid":226984,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"70c030a49c451d16796037706016066dd58915f5","tid":1845304,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續擴散，日本政府預料最快明日起派遣包機到中國武漢，接走滯留當地的日本人。共同社引述政府消息人士透露，當局正與中國政府協調，計劃從成田機場起降的方案，有需要的話亦會在包機飛往武漢時，向當地運送支援物資。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡教育部因應疫情，要求所有最近到過中國的學生與教職員，在家中自行隔離14日。<br />\n<br />\n另外，蒙古宣布即天起關閉與中國接壤的邊境通道，包括汽車和行人通道，又呼籲取消所有公眾集會，並關閉所有大學和教育機構，直至3月2日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505068-20200127.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505068-20200127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=9d2fec38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505068-20200127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e8bce45b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505068-20200127.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"41623805f85a0c92b6a9c6cc59c3fc48cfa7c9bf","tid":1845304,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:48:18.000Z","msg":"蒙古都好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03108890b6327ed4091a4a544804172e57e08949","tid":1845304,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:55:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE